            Sectarian violence in Syria
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image
          border-radius="10px"
          padding="10px 12px"
          width="600px"
          src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/bedouin-druze-clashes-suweida-al-maqwas.jpg"
